  npcName: Little Boy
  npcPortrait: {fileID: -7527145504033472756, guid: eb7c67ad43d260c4c9535c0cd9400365, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - "Congratulations on taking down General Volkov! That fight was no small feat,
    and you\u2019ve officially brought peace to one of the most haunted souls in
    the Buran Army."
  - This was once his childhood home. General Volkov was a truly happy man, but when
    the war broke out, he lost his entire family to the flames
  - "Consumed by grief, he enlisted in the army, where they performed horrific experiments
    on him\u2014turning him into more machine than man."
  - By defeating, you set his spirit free. Thanks for putting him to rest.
